Package: ExprX
Type: Package
Title: Interspecies differential expression analysis of orthologous
        genes
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mingan", "Sun", email="mingansun@yahoo.com", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Yejun", "Wang", role = c("ctb")),
    person("Linlin", "Zou", role = c("ctb")),
    person("Todd", "Macfarlan", role = c("ctb"))
    )
Maintainer: Ming-an Sun <mingansun@gmail.com>
Description: ExprX is a R package to streamline interspecies differential expression
    analysis. Taking TPM or FPKM/RPKM files for samples from different species as
    input, it provides functions to handle all necessary steps, including data loading,
    ortholog matching, normalization, differential analysis and visualization.
